<div style="max-width:740px;margin:0 auto;padding:3rem 1.5rem">
  <h1 style="font-size:2rem;font-weight:800;margin-bottom:1.5rem">Contact</h1>

  <p style="margin-bottom:1.25rem;line-height:1.75;font-size:1.125rem">Have a product you want us to review? Want to work together? We'd love to hear from you.</p>

  <p style="margin-bottom:1.25rem;line-height:1.75">Email us at <a href="mailto:contact@nickpicks.com" style="font-weight:600">contact@nickpicks.com</a> and we'll get back to you as soon as we can.</p>

  <h2 style="font-size:1.25rem;font-weight:700;margin:2.5rem 0 0.75rem">What We're Looking For</h2>
  <ul style="margin:0.75rem 0 1rem 1.5rem;line-height:1.75">
    <li><strong>Product reviews.</strong> If you make a product in our categories — home office, fitness, kitchen, beauty, or pet tech — and want honest, independent coverage, reach out. We can't guarantee a review or a positive outcome, but we read every pitch.</li>
    <li><strong>Affiliate &amp; brand partnerships.</strong> We work with brands whose products we'd genuinely recommend. If that sounds like you, tell us about what you're selling.</li>
    <li><strong>Reader questions.</strong> Can't decide between two products? Send us a note. We can't answer every email personally, but common questions often turn into articles.</li>
    <li><strong>Data requests.</strong> For privacy-related inquiries, see our <a href="{{ '/privacy/' | url }}">Privacy Policy</a>.</li>
  </ul>

  <div style="background:#f8fafc;border:1px solid #e2e8f0;border-radius:0.5rem;padding:1.5rem;margin-top:2rem">
    <p style="margin:0;line-height:1.75"><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:contact@nickpicks.com">contact@nickpicks.com</a></p>
    <p style="margin:0.5rem 0 0;color:#64748b;font-size:0.875rem">We typically reply within 2–3 business days.</p>
